{"about_the_game":"<i><strong>The Retirement Home is in chaos as the Old Folks have stopped taking their meds. </strong></i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/scooter_gif.gif?t=1722277989\" /><br><br>Stop the onslaught of doctors from reaching the medicine cabinet and putting you all down for a nap. <br><br>Defend your retirement home with a cast of quirky Old Folks. Plan your defenses carefully and try different strategies with the variety of towers and upgrades.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/desc_text_old_folk_towers.png?t=1722277989\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/newtowersvideo-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1722277989\" /><br><br>Each offensive tower you can place down is a different Old Folk each with their own strengths and weaknesses. <br><br><strong>Granny</strong> - Smacks the doctors with her trusty cane.<br><br><strong>Gramps</strong> - Throws slippers at the whippersnapper doctors with deadly accuracy.<br><br><strong>Poopy Pops</strong> - Poisons enemy doctors with his stinky fart attacks.<br><br><strong>Storytime Sally</strong> - Slows down enemies with her boring stories about the good old days.<br><br><strong>Crazy Carl</strong> - Throws explosive potions dealing splash damage.<br><br><strong>Boxer Bob</strong> - Throws heavy punches but has Alzheimer's and sometimes stuns nearby Old Folks.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/desc_text_multiple_maps.png?t=1722277989\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/new_maps_gif-min.gif?t=1722277989\" /><br><br>Choose from 7 uniquely designed levels. Change your strategy to suit each map and stop the doctors at all costs.<br><br>Levels:<br><br><strong>The Lounge</strong><br><br><strong>The Cafeteria</strong><br><br><strong>The Garden</strong><br><br><strong>The Hospital</strong><br><br><strong>The Basement</strong><br><br><strong>The Bingo Hall</strong><br><br><strong>The Swimming Pool</strong><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/desc_text_upgrade_your_old_folks.png?t=1722277989\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/upgrades_gif-min.gif?t=1722277989\" /><br><br>Watch the mayhem increase as you upgrade your Old Folks in hilarious ways to deal with more devastating enemies.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/desc_text_support_towers.png?t=1722277989\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/extras/support_tower_gif-min.gif?t=1722277989\" /><br><br>Choose from 4 support towers designed to support your Old Folks in unique ways. <br><br><strong>Meds Vending Machine</strong> - Dispenses &quot;special&quot; medications to nearby Old Folks which will get them feeling like they are 20 all over again, increasing their attack speed.<br><br><strong>Heater</strong> - Keep the nearby Old Folks bones warm and prevent them getting sick and stopping their attacks as often.<br><br><strong>Kamikaze Scooter </strong>- When things are desperate send a &quot;Kamikaze Scooter&quot; down the path to knock down the doctors in a high speed rampage.<br><br><strong>Bake Sale Stall</strong> - Sell &quot;Grandma's Baking&quot; to the passing doctors to earn passive income.<br><br><br><strong>More levels, old folks and doctor enemies coming soon!</strong>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379690/page_b